  "title": "Spring force - block on a spring in an elevator",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular chamber that contains a block of mass m connected to end of a vertical spring. The other end of the spring is attached to the ceiling of the chamber. The length of the spring is labeled x sub 1. A downward pointing arrow labeled Direction of Velocity is shown to the right of the chamber.\" src=\"/images/57da0f52444b2b106d02274493c4a66e.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A block of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\"><math alttext=\"m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>m</mi></math></span></span> hangs in equilibrium from an ideal spring inside an elevator, as shown. The elevator moves downward at a constant speed and the length of the spring is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x sub 1\"><math alttext=\"x sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>. The elevator then gradually slows to a stop with constant acceleration. Which of the following statements correctly describes the length of the spring while the elevator is decelerating?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i2",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It is constant and equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x sub 1\"><math alttext=\"x sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It is constant and greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x sub 1\"><math alttext=\"x sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It is constant and less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x sub 1\"><math alttext=\"x sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It starts off greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x sub 1\"><math alttext=\"x sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> and slowly decreases.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
  },
